佢復職..試問一個出賣客户資料既人,中令手足被捕,公司可以當冇事..<br />\n利申,Bonnie tong ,出名跑到數,佢係長沙灣同奥海城出名誤導銷售客戶,佢係5月時幫佢下屬sell 一個年長客户, 說服佢買UT基金,輸咗接近五成, 最仆街係叫sell d客向渣打Loan 錢,Loan完之後再幫佢買基金,佢為咗跑數 不擇手段 ,不停以欺詐手法銷售, 令到佢啲同事好驚畀人釘牌而唔敢出聲...<br />\n依加越爆越多野,公司反而保佢,同事們個個好驚比Bonnie 害死,佢不但出賣手足,中出賣同事,淨係識擦佢老闆Jo Tai 鞋,同埋同SME老闆Anthony 偷食..<br />\n希望各位手足幫手update 呢個post 上連登同各公海,唔該<br />\nJo Tai電話,大家可以去FC下<br />\n64686810<br />\n<br />\n左邊個個係Bonnie Tong,右邊個個就係Jo Tai"},{"pid":"540d66c9e76f5c4c5e0f945e1bd75f9c5683048f","tid":1758932,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06e39a0bd09476a7cd38476a3bc016167dd6fc22","tid":1758932,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"理得佢,一日唔炒條友一日都唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcca17608dd2276172b2788ebc064b20d75be1f","tid":1758932,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1088cadf6d74e694e2ed4f636bbe1c6f3735f51","tid":1758932,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e77e61e262bb6e5ed2ea959141c1345065d88dcb","tid":1758932,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2011290dafaae6e22163d90160dea8467ff9d5ae","tid":1758932,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"公信力...<br />\n唔怪得羅范話有天使 啲藍絲就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永久封鎖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋咁大間銀行<br />\n咁多監管機構<br />\n<br />\n兩樣嘢都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話去HKMA投訴<br />\n你睇下MA有冇出面啊<br />\n<br />\n冇啊嘛<br />\n啫係Fake News啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1